# Newsletter integration is optional. If unset, the API logs the email and
# returns success so the form keeps working in local dev.
#
# Set one of the following to actually capture subscribers:

# Generic webhook: receives JSON `{ "email": "..." }` via POST. Works with
# Zapier, Make.com, n8n, or any custom endpoint.
# NEWSLETTER_WEBHOOK_URL=

# Resend audience (https://resend.com): set both keys to add the email to
# an audience.
# RESEND_API_KEY=
# RESEND_AUDIENCE_ID=
